rComments: Teaching style is quite boring. She answers a lot of dumb questions in the lecture that ends up taking up most of the time. She tries to engage with the students but its generally boring. The tests and papers are okay and the content is interesting. I wouldn't take another course with her.
Great teacher. Great understanding of her subject area, very clear and not afraid to field questions. Not too hard, but you do need to do the readings. Textbook is just moderately useful.
